casa: CASA (Common Astronomy Software Applications)
casa:
casa:  CASA is the suite of C++ application libraries for the reduction and
casa:  analysis of radioastronomical data, packaged through a Python scripting
casa:  interface. CASA will be the primary off-line data reduction package for
casa:  both ALMA and the EVLA.
casa:
casa:  http://casa.nrao.edu/
casa: